  "translations": {
    "en": "So the Prophet (peace be upon him and his family) said: Get away from me, O wicked one! I fear that I will get burned by your fire. How near you are to the Fire! How near you are to the Fire! Then he (peace be upon him and his family) did not stop speaking and pointing at him until the youth left his presence. He went to Medina, gathered provisions from it, then went to one of its mountains to worship therein. He wore a hair cloak,",
